{
  "stem": "26790.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As he opened the door, I see about 15 or 50 Yiddish people sitting and singing songs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the-- on the table was still a few bottles of, of soft drinks, a few pieces of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's was-- according to Jewish religion, that's the third meal what Yiddish people have for Saturday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The first meal, they got on Friday night, second meal they got on Saturday, and the third meal, they got on Saturday between day and night.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not a special meal, just they dance, sing songs, like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As the man, Zalman-- You know, Zalman, the man, which-- which he repairman, he saw me, he stood up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He come to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He grab me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mojsze, forgive me my sins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What's that he done?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Zalman, what sin you done to me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forgive you, but-- but tell me what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I sinned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I did a sin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What sin you done?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he was coming my little workroom, he asked about a chuppah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I should shut the door and go, we fix it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't do like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I said, but Zalman, you're not ready, I'm not ready, and the people from the table wasn't.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Zalman, you see Mojsze is an honest-- honest man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I tell him, in a few weeks' time, we will have-- I, with my wife, will have the same day off.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'll make the chuppah at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went, save it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that day, when we talk about the chuppah we come there to have, a big table, with a white tablecloth cover, everything on the table what prepared for our [INAUDIBLE] something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Bread, [INAUDIBLE], fish, meat, vodka, everything, everything what you needed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell Leja where do I get it from?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
